runiface_104suz1665703180124.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/suz1665703180124.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/suz1665703180124.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"suz1665703180124\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Turn a string of 7 bytes into a DES key by adding an odd-parity bit for every 7 bits. The result is 8 bytes long; in each byte, the bit with the lowest significance is the parity bit.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"suz1665703180124__topic_d132758e1_d132759e1_d132760e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"suz1665703180124__p_d132761e1_d132762e1_d132763e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">extern void create_DESkey (unsigned char</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*String</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, unsigned char</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*DESkey</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">);</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"suz1665703180124__section_w4407ab1b5b3_w4408ab1b5_w4409ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90027e70\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Direction</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">7 byte string to be turned into DE key.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DESkey</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">OUT</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"suz1665703180124__table_d15836e1_d15837e1_d15838e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">8 byte DES key that can be used to encode and decode data using the\n                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">DESencrypt</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">DESdecrypt</code> functions.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"suz1665703180124__section_w4410ab1b5b5_w4411ab1b5_w4412ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90027e169\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"suz1665703180124__p_d132800e1_d132801e1_d132802e1\">Library <span class=\"ph filepath\">uenc</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"suz1665703180124__section_w4413ab1b5b7_w4414ab1b5_w4415ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90027e180\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"suz1665703180124__p_d132647e1_d132648e1_d132649e1\">This function is useful for creating security drivers\n        that need to encode and decode data.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ett